thread.title_full: Personalized Paper Manufacturing Group reviewed by Carolyn

author: Carolyn
title: Carolyn
text:
The ordering experience was quick and easy. I designed the first real thing I ever have on the computer with the help of the tutorials and was so happy with the results!
The 20lb Bond paper is a nice quality but next time I think I will trade up a notch to the 24lb.
